<subSubSection id="C368652E93588E05F2AAFA93FE17FAA8" pageId="1" pageNumber="485" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593588E05F2AAFA93FE17FAA8" blockId="1.[151,1436,1281,1488]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493588E05F2AAFA93FEE6FAD0" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[151,311,1281,1307]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean (1829)</bibRefCitation>
stated that he studied at least two individuals. The specimen designated as 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793588E05F645FA93FB0EFAD0" box="[1144,1247,1281,1307]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">lectotype</typeStatus>
is a female bearing the labels “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693588E05F301FAB4FE01FAF4" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[316,464,1318,1343]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Acupalpus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="485" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mauritanicus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793588E05F301FAB4FE01FAF4" box="[316,464,1318,1343]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">mauritanicus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
m. in Barbaria 
<collectingCountry id="F365763593588E05F047FAB7FD1CFAF4" box="[634,717,1317,1343]" name="Morocco" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">Tanger</collectingCountry>
”, “D. Solier” and “ 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793588E05F1A7FAB7FBDCFAF4" box="[922,1037,1317,1343]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">Lectotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693588E05F60DFAB7FF1EFAA8" authority="Dejean, 1829" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Acupalpus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="485" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mauritanicus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793588E05F60DFAB7FA91FAF4" box="[1072,1344,1317,1343]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">Acupalpus mauritanicus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493588E05F77BFAB7FF1EFAA8" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." pageId="1" pageNumber="485" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean, 1829</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
desig. by J. Serrano”.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C368652E93588E05F2FAFAFFFD77FA1B" pageId="1" pageNumber="485" type="reference_group">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593588E05F2FAFAFFFD77FA1B" blockId="1.[151,1436,1281,1488]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693588E05F2FAFAFFFE28FA4C" baseAuthorityName="Dejean" baseAuthorityYear="1829" box="[199,505,1389,1415]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Amblystomus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="485" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mauritanicus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793588E05F2FAFAFFFE28FA4C" box="[199,505,1389,1415]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">Amblystomus mauritanicus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is distributed in 
<collectingCountry id="F365763593588E05F081FAFCFCF0FA43" box="[700,801,1390,1416]" name="Morocco" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">Morocco</collectingCountry>
and western 
<collectingCountry id="F365763593588E05F187FAFFFC2AFA4C" box="[954,1019,1389,1415]" name="Georgia" pageId="1" pageNumber="485">Iberia</collectingCountry>
(Serrano, 2013), and is easily determined due to its large body size (
<quantity id="4C8A9B4093588E05F01DFA03FDAEFA67" box="[544,639,1425,1452]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.5" metricValueMax="6.0" metricValueMin="5.0" pageId="1" pageNumber="485" unit="mm" value="5.5" valueMax="6.0" valueMin="5.0">5-6 mm</quantity>
), slender antennae and asymmetrical labrum. Determination keys are available in 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493588E05F31DFA24FE6FFA04" author="Fuente de la, J. M." box="[288,446,1461,1488]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485" refId="ref10490" refString="Fuente de la, J. M. (1927) Tablas analiticas para la clasificacion de los coleopteros de la Peninsula Iberica. Adephaga: I Cicindelidae, II Carabidae. J. Bosch, Barcelona, 415 pp." type="book" year="1927">Fuente (1927)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493588E05F3CEFA27FD70FA1B" author="Antoine, M." box="[499,673,1461,1488]" pageId="1" pageNumber="485" pagination="315 - 465" refId="ref10238" refString="Antoine, M. (1959) Coleopteres Carabiques du Maroc. Troisieme partie. Memoires de la Societe des Sciences Naturelles et Physiques du Maroc, Nouvelle Serie, Zoologie, 6, 315 - 465." type="journal article" year="1959">Antoine (1959)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
